main event: Two objects similar to illuminated solid bodies or lights appeared and maneuvered in a zigzag manner in Homerville, Ohio.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 3 minutes., The objects were observed to be between 6 to 8 degrees in size., Observations included a soft grating noise associated with the objects., The objects disappeared over trees after constant observation., The report was part of the Project Blue Book.
sighted object: two illuminated solid bodies or lights
